           used  for  graphics  output, eg Sigmex ARGS 7000, then LSL$VS points to
           the parallel interface port to be used for  communication  with  it  eg
           IDA0:.

        o  LSL$SIGMA_COLOUR, LSL$TEK_COLOUR, LSL$VAX_COLOUR LSL$DECW_COLOUR  point
           to  the  colour  table definition file for the appropriate display type
