  8.6  [1mCUSTOMER[0m [1m-[0m [1mCustomer-Specific[0m [1mSoftware[0m

  Many LAMPS customers have a need for customer-specific software  to  tailor  the
  LAMPS  system  for  their  precise  application,  eg  to transfer map data to an
  external databank in a particular format.   Such  utilities  usually  require  a
  limited  environment  similar  to  that  of  IMP  (qv).   Any  customer-specific
  Laser-Scan logical names should  take  the  form  LSL$'customer'_'purpose'.   eg
  LSL$OS_CODES for customer OS (Ordnance Survey), code lookup file.


