           LITES2  guidance  command  file  produced  by  program RELHT in case of
           coding ambiguity.

        o  The current default directory of SYS$DISK:[] is  used  for  reading  an
           optional  file  containing  feature  code  pairs  (FCP file).  The same
           directory is used to create a saved  statistics  file  (ILINKSTAT.DAT).
